[[div class="warning-tide opener"]]
[[div_ class="warning-header"]]
**{{Diplomatic Report D-8710-02}}**
[[/div]]

[[span class="hili"]]Date:[[/span]] ██/██/████ 

[[span class="hili"]]Locations:[[/span]] Kutha, Iraq

[[span class="hili"]]Participants:[[/span]] Dr. Emily Kurr AKA SCP-8710-01 (reclassified to SCP-8710), Unknown Beast of Nature 'Abigail' (E-8710-02), Unknown Beast of Nature  'Aleah' (E-8710-03), O5-01-03 Dr. Sherry Andrews, Omega-12 ("Achilles Heels") and MTF Psi-8 ("The Silencers").

[[span class="hili"]]Foreword:[[/span]] Following meeting of the O5 council, and political lobbying, Dr. Andrews returned to Kutha to present a modified proposal to SCP-8710 and the two additional Beasts of Nature.

----
<Begin Log>

Dr. Andrews walks into the negotiation chamber with her accompanying retinue. SCP-8710-01 through -03 look up from the various positions in which they are seated upon the couches. She sits in place, picking up a plate of food and a cup full of wine.

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01:[[/span]] "Welcome back Dr. Andrews. We began to believe you would not return."

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "It's been an annoyingly long week. I'm not going to beat around the bush, the council did not like your proposal." 

E-8710-02 holds out a hand, and a very bright shaft of light forms in the obscured hand, as a noticeable blue-green fog begins to seep across the floors.

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01,-02,-03 in unison:[[/span]] "We see." 

Omega-12 and Psi-8 tense. 

Dr. Andrews holds up a hand. 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "So I made a modified proposal." 

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01:[[/span]] "Those were not the ter--"

[[span class="hili"]]E-8710-02:[[/span]] "Hush Emily, compromise is part of the game." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "It sure fucking is." 

[[span class="hili"]]E-8710-03:[[/span]] "Please continue." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "The Foundation will withdraw all surveillance resources from within Valencia... and Ibiza. You will have sole dominion over those areas, and we'll be declaring them free ports for anomalous individuals to live untouched. We will establish monitoring stations outside the bounds of your influence in the event of spillover. This will be the status quo as long as you do as you've offered in filtering any anomalous material off platforms that could leak to the outside world." 

[[span class="hili"]]E-8710-02:[[/span]] "I think that's acceptable, but I have a feeling you're not done." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "Correct."

Dr. Andrews crosses one leg over the other and has a sip of water from a canteen.

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "In addition to this, Dr. Sarkis will not be reinstated in her former position. Instead, she will be moved to my office, and serve as direct liaison between you, and any other surprise Beasts of Nature that happen to pop up, facilitating communication to me directly." 

SCP-8710-01 shifts in place.

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01:[[/span]] "These were not the terms but are an acceptable alternative." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "Good. Any further communication will be conducted under the confines of OPERATION HIGH TIDE. Additionally, while you initially offered information on the location of materials relevant to the Finnfolk, the council felt this was insufficient on its own to counterbalance the benefits you gain. We wish to gather some more information relevant to an operation occurring with an undercover member of the Serpent's hand who is planning to defect." 

E-8710-02 leans forward.

[[span class="hili"]]E-8710-02:[[/span]] "We have nothing to do with the Hand." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "But you do know about other mythological beings." 

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01:[[/span]] "We do, but what is the relevance?" 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "Two upcoming operations, with the latter one we believe being of interest to you." 

[[span class="hili"]]E-8710-03:[[/span]] "You're being cryptic." 

[[span class="hili"]]SCP-8710-01:[[/span]] "I am enjoying this, please finish." 

[[span class="hili"]]Dr. Andrews:[[/span]] "What do you know about Atalanta?" 

Dr. Andrews turns to the MTF operator handling the camera and makes a motion across her neck with her hand. The camera cuts off.

<End Recorded Log>

-----

[[span class="hili"]]Postword:[[/span]] Following the second diplomatic meeting, an official cooperative agreement was organized and signed recognizing Valencia and Ibiza as free ports for anomalous individuals. Foundation resources monitoring these locations were withdrawn and SCP-8710's documentation has been flagged for significant updates to reflect identification of the source of the anomaly, and the current hands-off containment protocols being enforced. 

Foundation agents have been implanted within the Horizon Initiative and upper echelons of the Catholic Church in an attempt to identify the source of deific interference detected in Incident Logs 1-3. 

Further inquiries should be addressed to O5-01's office at this time.
[[/div]]


